description:
Data set generated as part of a proof-of-concept analysis for verifying a PCR protocol for targeted amplicon sequencing of three of the four known  Plasmodium falciparum&nbsp; sickle-associated SNPs.&nbsp; 
 The data set includes sequencing files (.ab1), genotypes and metadata for 234 samples of  Plasmodium falciparum  DNA isolated from patient samples originating from Cameroon, Gabon, Nigeria, and Rwanda.&nbsp; 
 &nbsp;

